gnm:Cells.gnm:Cell: This table is the solution of a direct geodetic intersection by the known coordinates of the horizon of the stations (Y, X, H)
and certain directional and zenith angles (a, Z *).
DATA sheet - contains the known coordinates of the horizon of the stations (Y, X, H), certain directional and zenith angles (a, Z *) and basic calculations.
RESULT sheet - contains elements of the curvature of the Earth, the result of resection and its evaluation.
HOW TO: Angles in measurement results are presented in degrees with decimal places (as in most electronic total station files).
